data.description: Gorgeous home with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and 2 car garage in central location in Chesapeake and only 2 YEARS Old.  Open design downstairs, will all bedrooms of large size. Huge Primary Bedroom with double vanity and over-sized walk in  closet. Granite in kitchen and baths, stainless steel appliances, and so much more. Brand New Solar Panels installed. A  beautiful backyard that allows for all kinds of social events! Seller willing to provide Closing Cost Assistance.
